<br>
I was heavy into trade skills on that server too.  I had just fashioned some new armor and wanted to advertise a bit.  I planned to go afk for a while.  Instead of logging out I went afk while sitting on a post on top of a balcony overhanging a common walkway in East Cabilis.  I figured people would con me as they walked by and might ask where they could get some armor like mine.  I left the computer...<br>
<br>
I returned about 30 minutes later just in time to see myself die.  How you ask?  I was killed by a Froglok Slave!  <br>
<br>
Apparently some noob was fighting the frogs near the Toilmaster there in town.  The noob died but the frog was still mad.  It noticed me sitting on the post and decided to attack.<br>
<br>
I scrolled back and saw he had missed me over 100 times before he finally hit me for 2 points of damage.  When something hits you you are moved just a bit.  His single hit was enough to bump me off of my perch.  Since I was sitting just over the water I fell in.<br>
<br>
I returned to my computer just in time to hear my last gulp of water and was staring right into the face of the Froglok Slave.  He hit me one time through the whole thing.<br>
<br>
I am probably the only lvl 40 SHM to ever manage to get killed by a lvl 1 mob.   &lt;sigh&gt;<br>
<br>
Jehryn <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uazhreihieverdphlith.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Azhrei Hiever dPhlith</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Punter of Gnomes<br>Stealer of Dorfpickles<br>Master of Apep<br>ManWithReallyLongTitle</span><br>  Posts: 66<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(4/22/02 3:45:29 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=433.topic&index=55>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Worst/Funniest death you either watched or had happen to</span><hr size=1> Funniest:  Fly-by-rez, Fear CR(TM).   I'm sure somewhere, someone has done something similar to this, but far as I know I'm the only one to do it quite this crazy..  On occasions where a fear raid has wiped out on north wall and no clerics made camp-out, rather than waste time on a lengthy CR I'll do this:<br>
